{"type": "article", "id": 29522, "title": "看图：这里是过去24小时内发生的重要的事", "description": "每天我们都会摘取重要的新闻图片。PS：我们认为这个世界的重要性不应该有绝对的等级，重点是看得更多，探索更多。", "date": "2016-07-13T02:21:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 5, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160713094203Vo3uPA1Bs0k5rOWn.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><h3>过去的一段时间里，你需要知道的有：</h3><p><b>1、意大利发生火车对撞事故</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713090323kY5GnArCKMoEQ2qZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.602857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">意大利东南部濒亚德里亚海的普里亚省（Puglia）发生火车对撞事故，目前已经导致至少 20 人死亡 34 人受伤。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>2、巴西里约奥运大道仍在施工</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713093654dZivajzb5rtwOsF3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666281\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Luiz Souza/NurPhoto/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">巴西里约热内卢，数十名工人在奥林匹克大道施工。这里曾是治安混乱的港口区，现在正在建设轻轨与机场和公交总站接驳。著名艺术家 Kobra 会在大道的围墙上绘制面积达 3000 平米的涂鸦。<br></p><p><b>3、乌克兰民众抗议议会休会</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713092250uKfbSaoEZtlT6Hx3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Valentyn Ogirenko/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">乌克兰基辅，民众在议会大楼前支起沙滩椅晒太阳，抗议议会休会。<br></p><p><b>4、美国民众持续抗议警察射杀非裔男子</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607130934533sPMUVahCyONL2vm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Shannon Stapleton/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">美国路易斯安那州巴吞鲁日，民众在市政厅前游行，抗议警察枪杀非裔男子。<b><br></b></p><p><b>5、印尼民众聚集火山口围观火山喷发</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607130926202VqtuPA1yCEKzOUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">印度尼西亚普罗博林戈（Probolinggo），布罗莫火山（Bromo）爆发，当地民众聚集在火山口进行围观。</p><h3>除此之外，这些也值得一看：</h3><p class=\"\"><b>1、2017 春夏纽约男装周</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713100839wosmWaSqF8e4V2kL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504274\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Jonas Gustavsson/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">Joseph Abboud 品牌秀场。<b><br></b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607130957262kmPZljGsrdUfSNu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664828\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Jonas Gustavsson/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">Tim Coppens 品牌秀场。<b><br></b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713095457XkZTCUObslfMjIBN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Randy Brooke/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">Robert Geller 品牌秀场。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713095859JTLDsKz3ac6GY5Vw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.450677\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Daniel Zuchnik/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607131000218mw6qfaHtZXo2GKF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.452785\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Daniel Zuchnik/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713100948YuN37aT80oSLA9QM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Daniel Zuchnik/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">街头潮人云集。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>2、英国“第一猫”留任</b><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713093020tNU8WoVcuQkGfpmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Jeff J Mitchell/Getty Images/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">英国伦敦，内阁办公室首席捉鼠猫“拉里”坐在唐宁街 10 号前。拉里将在卡梅伦 7 月 13 日搬出首相府后<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-politics-36772515\" rel=\"nofollow\">继续留任</a>。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>3、沙滩、爱犬和酒吧</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607131006096bjfKds1wSrHxQel.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Antonio Bronic/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">克罗地亚茨里克韦尼察（Crikvenica），克罗地亚第一家专门为宠物狗设计的沙滩酒吧正在营业。这家酒吧为宠物狗提供特别准备的冰淇淋、啤酒和小吃，使狗狗和主人可以在海滩上同享惬意时刻。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>4、曼哈顿“悬日”</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713090905BURyoGVSj07Fc4AJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666571\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Mark Kauzlarich/路透社/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">美国纽约，民众争相拍摄“曼哈顿悬日”奇观。<br></p><p class=\"\"><b>5、猎户座星云</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><b></b><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713090647XNj6KY9gcaBWtvmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.758042\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">H. DRASS/视觉中国</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">欧洲南方天文台发布猎户座星云图片。这张照片是该区域纵深最深、呈现行星团最多的图像。<b><br></b></p>"}